text: Melissa Suzanne George (born 6 August 1976) is an Australian actress. She played Angel Parrish in Home and Away. She then moved to the United States. After that, she acted in Friends, Grey's Anatomy and In Treatment. George was born in Perth, Western Australia. ==References== Category:1976 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from Perth, Western Australia Category:Australian movie actors Category:Australian television actors
